	* src/plparse/totem-pl-parser-features.h: 
	* src/plparse/totem-pl-parser.h: 
	* src/plparse/Makefile.am:
	* src/plparse/.cvsignore: 
	* configure.in:
	Add mechanism to publish version and capabilities.
	(Closes: #326963)

