	* configure.in:
	* src/backend/gstscreenshot.c:
	  GStreamer-0.9 is dead, long live GStreamer-0.10! Grab the prerelease
	  now if you don't have it yet. Purge all mention of 0.9 and require
	  --enable-gstreamer=0.10.

