	* src/bacon-video-widget-gst.c: (bacon_video_widget_set_tv_out):
	For all the supported TV-Out types, we don't need a restart
	* src/totem-preferences.c: (on_tvout_toggled): don't hard-code
	dxr3 needing a restart

