	* NEWS: upd
	* src/totem-pl-parser.c: (totem_pl_parser_parse_internal),
	(totem_pl_parser_parse): We now can recurse into 3 levels of
	subdirectories (enough for drag'n'dropping, say, an "iTunes Music"
	directory) (Closes: #149173)

